.EC

.SP 5 5
Each player will usually join a guild so that they can learn skills
and commands and so advance their abilities.   Being in a guild also
adds character to your character.

These guilds are currently available:
.EP
.SO 5 20 -30
	Assasssins' Guild	is located at the eastern end of Filigree Street.  Fill in an application and give it to the secretary in the guild office.
	
	Thieves' Guild	is at the beginning of Alchemist Street.
	
	Priests' Guild	with its various gods is located on Small Gods Street.  Deities include: Hat, Pishe, Fish, Sek, Gapp, Gufnork and Sandelfon.  For more information try 'finger <deity>' or 'info' in their guild room.
	
	Warriors' Guild	is on Filigree Street, just a stone's throw from Mended Drum.
	
	Witches' Guild	is located at Granny Weatherwax' cottage in Lancre.  See Gennie Applebottom at Dione Street in Ankh-Morpork if you have trouble finding the place.
	
	Wizards' Guild	is located west of Sator Square.  To join you have to look around in the Great Hall and find a staircase.
.EO
